manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: What's in the Box: Glade Solid Air Freshener, Cashmere Woods, 6 Ounces. Glade Solid Air Freshener, Cashmere Woods The Glade Solid Air Freshener is the perfectly practical way to add continuous fragrance to your home with a variety of scents to choose from. Simply twist to release the rich fragrance within and set the intensity by adjusting the lid. Available in a wide variety of rich fragrances at a great value Can be easily placed anywhere in the home for continuous freshness Simple to use with no outlets or batteries needed Adjustable cone allows you to release just the right amount of fragrance for your home

Cashmere Woods Notes of citrus and jasmine and the oaky scents of amber and vanilla beans capture the essence of a luxurious fall day with Glade Cashmere Woods. This rustic retreat surrounds you in the comforts of wooded bliss in the coziest season.

Clean Floral Fruity Gourmet Outdoor Tropical Open up to scent and find your perfect Glade product. LIFE. We have a fragrance for that. These fragrances harness the energy of a fresh, gentle breeze to take your home from lived-in comfort to loved-up care. Fresh-cut fragrances move the air from unremarkable to full of life. Capture the essence of fruit picked at the peak of deliciousness. Fruity fragrances power daily life from routine to a moment ripe with refreshment. The cozy scent of delectable treats instantly takes your space from house to home, sweet-smelling home. Elements from nature move from outside to indoors to revitalize your natural habitat. Go from the daily grind to lei’d back leisure. Sweet fruit and fragrant flowers awaken the senses with a tropical punch.

A Product For Every Moment Every Glade product brings true-to-life fragrance to your home, available in a variety of options from premium room sprays to candles, scented oils and more. Look for all of your favorites in our new packaging.

Use in any room where continuous fragrance is needed. Directions: Tear away wrap at the bottom where marked 'peel and tear here to open'. Twist and lift cap to activate. Place solid air freshener anywhere in your home to enjoy continuous freshness.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Based on Experience
reviews.reviewText: The ratings are based on long experience with this product.So far as I can tell, this is the Glade that you unwrap and prop open. It then slowly perfuses the air, providing its function, until only the central stem is left. Then you get rid of it.Why it is said to be powered by anything, even a battery, is unclear to me.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars The scent is so faint it doesn't help with odors!
reviews.reviewText: This is a great scent in other glade products, so I was looking forward to it. But, in this solid form you can barely smell anything at all. VERY disappointing! Back to the sprays.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Colored glob of brown goo.
reviews.reviewText: No fragrance, no ordor elimination, nothing.The spray smells wonderful, but even with my nose nearly touching the goop there is no fragrance and the odors lingered as if it wasn't inches from them.I also had to use a toothpick to keep it open.I'll be sticking with the spray and never trying a stick again from now on.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love Cashmere Woods above any other scent. I could describe it about 50 words. It’s just so captivating. The scent teavelsxin a big room. I love to come home; open the door and the scent is there. It’s relaxing

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2016
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing, almost manly
reviews.reviewText: My mom used to get these types of air fresheners a lot when I was young and they always seemed to have the same generic flowery cheap bathroom spray smell to them but this scent is absolutely divine.I'd describe it as a naturally fresh and clean yet warm smell. Simple yet bold but not overpowering nor fragrancy and flowery. I'm not sure if this is what cashmere smells like, but I love it. It has a particular note that I've smelled in a nice cologne or body wash or similar before, can't remember at all but it rings a bell. Wish I had ordered more when they were on sale for $1.Will fill a large room and lasts much longer than cheaper versions. Love the smell so much, not perfumey at all, I think most guys would really like this one compared to most other scents.
Glade never disappoints when it comes to their products. Thumbs up for this one.
